5 0.02414652332663536 [ORIENTATION] Til, Pan, Roll: 0.19543787837028503 0.02197265625 0.02471373975276947 [ORIENTATION] Til, Pan, Roll: 0.19867371022701263 0.02197265625 0.0238236952573061\n\nResult:\n\n## Author\n\n    \n    \n    github: winter2897 mail: haiquantran2897@gmail.com\n\n## About\n\nPython sample control gimbal via Mavlink\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nApache-2.0 license\n\nActivity\n\nCustom properties\n\n### Stars\n\n10 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n1 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n0 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases\n\nNo releases published\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Languages\n\n  * Shell 69.7%\n  * Python 30.3%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
